title: Tsu Hsiang
description: Previously a restaurant, but as of Jan 2016 offering delivery only. Dishes such as enchiladas, rice and noodle, sausages, soups, peanuts, vegetal steaks and faux meat, salads. No eggs used but some items contain cheese. Please update HappyCow of changes.
streetAddress: Avenida El Progreso, De Banpro 25 vrs. al Sur.
